XMI.documentation.XMI.longDescription: The MOF provides a set of modeling elements, including rules for their use, with which to construct models. Formally, the MOF is defined in itself: in essence the MOF Model is its own metamodel. This file contains the MOF PrimitiveTypes package expressed as a MOF metamodel. This file is non-normative.
XMI.documentation.XMI.shortDescription: Definition of the PrimitiveTypes package for MOF version 1.4, generated according to XMI version 1.1.
